{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Toziuha Night is a 2D side-scrolling action platformer with features of a <strong>metroidvania RPG</strong>. Travel through different non-linear maps set in a <strong>dark fantasy world</strong>; such as a gloomy forest, demon-infested dungeons, a ruined village and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112750/extras/banner_1.gif?t=1729632290\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Xandria, a beautiful and skilled alchemist who, using an iron whip, fights against the most fearsome demons and other alchemists seeking to obtain a millenary power. To accomplish her mission, <strong>Xandria will use various chemical elements to perform powerful attacks and spells.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112750/extras/banner_2.GIF?t=1729632290\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112750/extras/banner_0.png?t=1729632290\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Original symphonic music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro pixelart style as a tribute to 32-bit consoles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your skills by fighting final bosses and various enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore new areas of the map using different skills and improving your stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play without internet connection (offline game).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Anime and Gothic style characters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compatible with gamepads. (even generic gamepads with an extra configuration)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine iron with other chemical elements to create alloys with different playable properties.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A map with a minimum of 7 hours of gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Any player will be able to design their own map (mods), other players will be able to download it and play.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More playable characters with different gameplay mechanics.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112750/extras/banner_3.GIF?t=1729632290\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Attack of the Dead Men","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/b88aae9d7ab99c8a18620121e818870cd0d8f09b.jpg"},{"name":"The Radium Witch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/6b2d8e3f1b8ac6bf47a75ef41248edd2837e3c89.jpg"},{"name":"Travel on the Orient Express","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/dc251a33b37b24a87988c37f7de33601fa9045c2.jpg"},{"name":"Oxygenium Adeptis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/dec772641ca0da564c5967842e746581946c95ba.jpg"},{"name":"Crux simplex ad infixionem","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/1f06ca6cbcd171159919e4dc9f2f3f41b4a97835.jpg"},{"name":"Critical mass","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/b6bd199452a21ad43afa05504bb333adb2794691.jpg"},{"name":"Vela del Candil","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/08cbbee69fae2662679825e696e503d12b249f8d.jpg"},{"name":"Chrysopoeia ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/15ac5a519592e1bcf4f1b003cf96a90b337b5793.jpg"},{"name":"Nitrum Adeptis","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2112750/ca237f09d21352868fd3d79184f97bf7c8ebf107.jpg"},{"